			<div class="post-923 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-art category-electronics category-history-2 category-literary category-maths category-science category-technology tag-arto-heino tag-circuit tag-individualization tag-nikola-tesla tag-recieving tag-transmitter" id="post-923">
				<h2><a href="http://artojh.wordpress.com/2014/03/22/art-of-individualization/" rel="bookmark">Tesla&#8217;s Art of Individualization</a></h2>
				<small>March 22, 2014 </small>

				<div class="entry">
