				<h2><a href="http://artojh.wordpress.com/2014/03/14/synthonyms-vi/" rel="bookmark">Synthonyms VI</a></h2>
				<small>March 14, 2014 </small>

				<div class="entry">
					<p>Here are some more retakes on some major players in the world game of misinformation. &#8220;Moral Blank&#8221;, Working for a World full of Poverty. The goal of the World bank was to eliminate poverty, to be honest since it has made this pledge poverty has grown, the new wording has been its primary objective and its has proven a success.</p>
<p><a href="http://artojh.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/worldb1a.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-861" alt="Moral Blank" src="http://artojh.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/worldb1a.jpg?w=450&#038;h=533" width="450" height="533" /></a></p>
<p>A new level of EWES(news) and ENTRAINMENT(entertainment) to DEFORM(inform) your daily life.- &#8220;FAKETEL&#8221;</p>
<p><a href="http://artojh.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/foxtel1e.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-862" alt="FAKETEL" src="http://artojh.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/foxtel1e.jpg?w=450&#038;h=112" width="450" height="112" /></a></p>
<p>This is the Political Party(Liberal) that spawned our current Fuhrer of Australia Tony Abbott.</p>
<p><a href="http://artojh.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/liberal1c.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-863" alt="Lie Brawl Party" src="http://artojh.files.wordpress.com/2014/03/liberal1c.jpg?w=450&#038;h=374" width="450" height="374" /></a>Please enjoy, Regards Arto.</p>
